Detailed Description

cvmx_agl_gmx_bad_reg

AGL_GMX_BAD_REG = A collection of things that have gone very, very wrong

Notes: OUT_OVR[0], LOSTSTAT[0], OVRFLW, TXPOP, TXPSH will be reset when MIX0_CTL[RESET] is set to 1. OUT_OVR[1], LOSTSTAT[1], OVRFLW1, TXPOP1, TXPSH1 will be reset when MIX1_CTL[RESET] is set to 1. STATOVR will be reset when both MIX0/1_CTL[RESET] are set to 1.
